column5: Hey guys.  Just wondering if anyone knew when the Lake Simcoe ice fishing derby is.  I know there are a few that happen, but I was looking for the one thats out of Virginia Beach.  Went to it a few years back, so im not 100% sure its still around.  Thanks
Found this listing with a few derbies http://www.fishingderbyonline.com/DerbySearch?countryFilter=Canada
